{"id":"skin-coats-made-of","term":"Skin, Coats made of","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 3:21\">Gen. 3:21</a>). Skins of rams and badgers were used as a covering for the tabernacle (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 25:5\">Ex. 25:5</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 4:8\">Num. 4:8-14</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 3:21","Exodus 25:5","Numbers 4:8"]}